{"content": "<p><em><a href=\"https://opensea.io/collection/geodetica\">Purchase a Geodetica</a> by MintFace for 0.05 eth. </em></p><blockquote class=\"kg-blockquote-alt\">\"Geodetica documents the shortest visual path between human and machine. AI was invited to interpret 100 artwork titles from the Geodetic Moments collection minted a year ago\" says MintFace.</blockquote><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://opensea.io/collection/geodetica\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">View Collection on OpenSea</a></div><figure class=\"kg-card kg-gallery-card kg-width-wide kg-card-hascaption\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-container\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-row\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2022/08/37_mintface.eth_All_you_need_is_willpower._Once_that_runs_out..._a_68f36ce2-8d12-4eaa-b324-b9959dfdcb08.png\" width=\"1664\" height=\"1664\" loading=\"lazy\" alt srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w600/2022/08/37_mintface.eth_All_you_need_is_willpower._Once_that_runs_out..._a_68f36ce2-8d12-4eaa-b324-b9959dfdcb08.png 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1000/2022/08/37_mintface.eth_All_you_need_is_willpower._Once_that_runs_out..._a_68f36ce2-8d12-4eaa-b324-b9959dfdcb08.png 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1600/2022/08/37_mintface.eth_All_you_need_is_willpower._Once_that_runs_out..._a_68f36ce2-8d12-4eaa-b324-b9959dfdcb08.png 1600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2022/08/37_mintface.eth_All_you_need_is_willpower._Once_that_runs_out..._a_68f36ce2-8d12-4eaa-b324-b9959dfdcb08.png 1664w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></div><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2022/08/76_mintface.eth_Silhouettes_of_a_young_boy_what_might_have_been._T_7926dec8-16b7-418f-a96c-f14de8a9c8c3.png\" width=\"1664\" height=\"1664\" loading=\"lazy\" a