_in_the_way_or_is_your_shadow_the_wa_9f2de002-f954-44da-b64a-7136e1c32db7.png\" width=\"1664\" height=\"1664\" loading=\"lazy\" alt srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w600/2022/08/9_mintface.eth_Is_your_shadow_in_the_way_or_is_your_shadow_the_wa_9f2de002-f954-44da-b64a-7136e1c32db7.png 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1000/2022/08/9_mintface.eth_Is_your_shadow_in_the_way_or_is_your_shadow_the_wa_9f2de002-f954-44da-b64a-7136e1c32db7.png 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1600/2022/08/9_mintface.eth_Is_your_shadow_in_the_way_or_is_your_shadow_the_wa_9f2de002-f954-44da-b64a-7136e1c32db7.png 1600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2022/08/9_mintface.eth_Is_your_shadow_in_the_way_or_is_your_shadow_the_wa_9f2de002-f954-44da-b64a-7136e1c32db7.png 1664w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></div><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2022/08/11_mintface.eth_The_ordinary_might_be_expected_as_you_revisit_the__06c6aa0e-538d-4f50-9f29-974d387b5dd4.png\" width=\"1664\" height=\"1664\" loading=\"lazy\" alt srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w600/2022/08/11_mintface.eth_The_ordinary_might_be_expected_as_you_revisit_the__06c6aa0e-538d-4f50-9f29-974d387b5dd4.png 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1000/2022/08/11_mintface.eth_The_ordinary_might_be_expected_as_you_revisit_the__06c6aa0e-538d-4f50-9f29-974d387b5dd4.png 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1600/2022/08/11_mintface.eth_The_ordinary_might_be_expected_as_you_revisit_the__06c6aa0e-538d-4f50-9f29-974d387b5dd4.png 1600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2022/08/11_mintface.eth_The_ordinary_might_be_expected_as_you_revisit_the__06c6aa0e-538d-4f50-9f29-974d387b5dd4.png 1664w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></div></div></div><figcaption>Geodetica collection</figcaption></figure><h2 id=\"geodetica-collection\">Geodetica Collection</h2><p>The Geodetica collection asks AI to reinterpret the very first collection I minted using only the description of each artwork as the base material. Each NFT includes the prompt that created the artwork so you can attempt to recreate, remix and relive your own Geodetic Moment.</p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://opensea.io/collection/geodetica\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">View Collection on OpenSea</a></div><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><a href=\"https://opensea.io/collection/geodetica\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2022/08/Screen-Shot-2022-08-12-at-3.22.32-PM.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1564\" height=\"1012\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w600/2022/08/Screen-Shot-2022-08-12-at-3.22.32-PM.png 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1000/2022/08/Screen-Shot-2022-08-12-at-3.22.32-PM.png 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2022/08/Screen-Shot-2022-08-12-at-3.22.32-PM.png 1564w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></a><figcaption><a href=\"https://opensea.io/collection/geodetica\">Geodetica collection</a></figcaption></figure><hr /><h3 id=\"what-frens-are-saying\">What Frens Are Saying</h3><p>Geodetica is the first of its kind AI derived collection… …drawing prompt inspiration from artwork descriptions created a year ago.…in a first for an NFT collection… …to layer up an entirely new collection. Here are what frens are saying:</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">My Geodetica #26 - awesome atmosphere - at least I feel it represents some of the best sea sunset views I’ve seen around the world all in one picture 🤩🔥🥰 <a href=\"https://t.co/jOmqrdksZx\">https://t.co/jOmqrdksZx</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/kSeti0QjzI\">pic.twitter.com/kSeti0QjzI</a></p>&mdash; B.F.G. ⌐◨-◨ 🔮🔺 (BrightFutureGuy. ΞTH) (@BrightFutureGuy) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/BrightFutureGuy/status/1557657397975519232?ref_src=twsrc%5E\ntfw\">August 11, 2022</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">&quot;An empty seat. An empty feeling. The shadows sometimes hang heavier.&quot;<br /><br />An honor to be among your collectors <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mintfaced?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@mintfaced</a> and congratz on the success on &quot;Geodetica&quot;&#39;s release! <a href=\"https://t.co/bapzJvuk1x\">pic.twitter.com/bapzJvuk1x</a></p>&mdash; zamunda.eth (@AbuSpinky) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/AbuSpinky/status/1557859676800303104?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">August 11, 2022</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">gm ☀️<br /><br />Happy to add Geodetica #60 by <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mintfaced?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@mintfaced</a> and AI. <br /><br />“Where the sky begins and the clouds end the earth always rises to meet. We get to play our lives in the middle.” <br /><br />Do you get what the AI is observing? 👀 <a href=\"https://t.co/eKrYRmhVag\">pic.twitter.com/eKrYRmhVag</a></p>&mdash; ParaChica (@parabolichica) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/parabolichica/status/1557660852588879873?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">August 11, 2022</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card kg-card-hascaption\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Introducing the Geodetica Collection by <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mintfaced?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@mintfaced</a> <br /><br />1/2 <a href=\"https://t.co/lE1kDmpj4M\">pic.twitter.com/lE1kDmpj4M</a></p>&mdash; MintFace 🍒 (@mintfaced) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mintfaced/status/1557643421615271936?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">August 11, 2022</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script><figcaption>`</figcaption></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2022/08/Screen-Shot-2022-08-12-at-3.18.47-PM.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1196\" height=\"1168\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w600/2022/08/Screen-Shot-2022-08-12-at-3.18.47-PM.png 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1000/2022/08/Screen-Shot-2022-08-12-at-3.18.47-PM.png 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2022/08/Screen-Shot-2022-08-12-at-3.18.47-PM.png 1196w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><hr /><h3 id=\"geodetica-availability\">Geodetica Availability</h3><p>There are 100 artworks in the <a href=\"https://opensea.io/collection/geodetica\">Geodetica collection</a>. </p><p>66 have sold. 35 are listed and available including:</p><p><em>#9 \"Is your shadow in the way or is your shadow the way? Don't be afraid to step into your whole self. You get to be part of the forming landscape too.\"<br />#14 \"Why are you not here yet?\"<br />#25 \"The path is long and winding.\"<br />#61 \"You might see one person in the distance on the path. That is enough to know you are not alone.\"<br />#69 \"Remember that. Focus in on the details.\"<br />#73 \"It isn't the view, it is the lines and the colours that make the moment.\"<br />#83 \"A devastating volcanic eruption also brings burnt ochre to our skies.\"<br />#91 \"The home straight. You could be anywhere.\"<br /></em></p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2022/08/geodetica-progress-email.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1200\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w600/2022/08/geodetica-progress-email.jpg 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1000/2022/08/geodetica-progress-email.jpg 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2022/08/geodetica-progress-email.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption>Geodetica Availability</figcaption></figure><hr /><h2 id=\"collection-technicals\">Collection Technicals</h2><p>Collection: <a href=\"https://opensea.io/collection/geodetica\">Geodetica</a><br />Artworks: 100 1/1s<br />Price: 0.05 eth </p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://opensea.io/collection/geodetica\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">View Collection on OpenSea</a></div><p>Smart Contract: Manifold <a href=\"https://etherscan.io/address/0xf6f44f3dde8ea78a3f49f78eeca339ffa17b2933\">0xf6f44f3dde8ea78a3f49f78eeca339ffa17b2933</a></p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2022/08/Screen-Shot-2022-08-12-at-3.39.34-PM.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1432\" height=\"308\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w600/2022/08/Screen-Shot-2022-08-12-at-3.39.34-PM.png 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1000/2022/08/Screen-Shot-2022-08-12-at-3.39.34-PM.png 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2022/08/Screen-Shot-2022-08-12-at-3.39.34-PM.png 1432w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption>Geodetica Smart Contract on Manifold</figcaption></figure><h2 id=\"geodetica-competition\">Geodetica Competition</h2><p>Be in to win a Geodetica artwork of your choice:</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">🚨 Giving away a Geodetica 🚨<br /><br />To enter: <br /><br />🍒 RT<br />🍒 Tag no one<br /><br />That’s it. Drawn in 42.69 hours. <a href=\"https://t.co/VxUXOsI5Yz\">pic.twitter.com/VxUXOsI5Yz</a></p>&mdash; MintFace 🍒 (@mintfaced) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mintfaced/status/1557837443558039552?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">August 11, 2022</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></figure><hr /><p></p>"}